text: Parkano is a town in Pirkanmaa, Finland. 6,071 people live there as of December 2024. Neighbouring municipalities are Ikaalinen, Jämijärvi, Kankaanpää, Karvia, Kihniö, Kurikka and Ylöjärvi. Most people speak Finnish. == Other websites == * Town of Parkano – Official website Category:Municipalities of Pirkanmaa
